<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Congratulations <%= User.find(@listing.user_id).firstname %> !</h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully added your listing to BarBnB.
      Its ID is:  <%= @listing.id %>.<br>
      Its Description is: <%= @listing.description %><br>
      And its price is <b><%= @listing.price_per_night %></b>
    </p>
    <p>
      To login to the site, just follow this link: <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>